		<credit project="CfPBoK@https://slebok.github.io/cfpbok/"/>
		<h1>Tag <code>T6B</code>: Industrial</h1>
		Work whose centre is industrial application of SLE: industrial case studies, adoption in production settings, constraints and practices specific to industry, and reports emphasising industrial impact. User studies with industrial participants can be tagged primary with <a href="t5h.html">T5H</a> or <a href="t6a.html">T6A</a>.
